16
00:04:02,633 --> 00:04:04,500
I just followed my belief.

17
00:04:04,500 --> 00:04:06,567
Don't say such a thing.

18
00:04:06,567 --> 00:04:09,400
If you risk your life over small matters, you'll end up ruining big things.

19
