Don't move.

22
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:26,500
Go.

23
00:04:26,500 --> 00:04:28,567
Jae Hoon.

24
00:04:37,333 --> 00:04:39,800
I said, go, you punk!

25
00:04:47,500 --> 00:04:49,433
Please.

26
00:04:49,433 --> 00:04:51,700
Let Seung Tae go.

27
